highlights.text: Taylor Swift has the most spots on Top Songs USA. “Cruel Summer” is the highest at #23.
“One Of The Girls (with JENNIE, Lily Rose Depp)” by The Weeknd, JENNIE, and Lily-Rose Depp is the biggest gainer on Top Songs USA, up 68 spots at #77.
“Needle (feat. Drake)” by Nicki Minaj and Drake is the highest new entry on Top Songs USA at #26.
“No Role Modelz” by J. Cole has been on Top Songs USA the longest, at 186 weeks straight.
